Package it.polimi.ingsw.client.controller

Class ClientManager

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.client.controller.ClientManager
public class ClientManager extends Object
The ClientManager acts as a controller layer above the UserInterface. Here there are the methods to initialize the different UIs.
Author:
Daniele Ferrario, Luca Guffanti
